Package: passwd-games
Version: 20131113
Revision: 1
Description: User/group for the games-files
Type: nosource
License: Public Domain
Maintainer: Fink Core Group <fink-core@lists.sourceforge.net>
Depends: passwd-core (>= 20130103-1)
CompileScript: <<
	### Get the docfiles from passwd-core
	cp -p %p/share/doc/passwd-core/README* .
<<
InstallScript: /usr/bin/true
DocFiles: README README.removing-users
PostInstScript: <<
	### <script> username 'Real Name' home shell groupname 'Group membership string'
	%p/sbin/update-passwd games 'Game Files Owner' /dev/null /dev/null games games
<<
DescDetail: <<
This package adds administrative user and group entries for the
"games" user to your user database. These are needed to
protect the data used by various games.
<<
